OL,4,G0205FMurder Scene: The Incident Room
OL,5,     GIn Swindon, 60-year-old Tom
OL,6,     GRogers was brutally stabbed by a
OL,7,     Gstranger. Investigators piece
OL,8,     Gtogether every shred of evidence
OL,9,     Gto see whether the killer has
OL,10,     Gattacked before.
OL,11,G0305FMurdered At First Sight
OL,12,     GOn July 4, 2017 Jorge Rodriguez
OL,13,     Gis shot while buying tomatoes for
OL,14,     Ga family event in Washington. He
OL,15,     Gdies seeking help. Days later, 17-
OL,16,     Gyear-old Pedro Cardenas is
OL,17,     Garrested after a tip-off.
